title: Hear Skrillex Reunite With From First To Last On “Make War”
text: Today is Skrillex's birthday -- happy birthday, Skrillex! -- and to celebrate, he's reunited with his former band for the first time in 10 years. The EDM superstar fronted the emo band From First To Last for a few years in mid-2000s, and they've teamed up once again on a new surprise single called "Make … More »
